{"tid":665182,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"好笑之原來我roommate 係大陸人","createTime":"2018-05-14T17:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T18:37:50.000Z","uid":161659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9e3725546882aeee492be9f3cb0483a7d8e13a","tid":665182,"uid":161659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:07:08.000Z","msg":"我有個好笑嘅笑話:<br />\n<br />\n我有個朋友，佢roommate 由sem2開始reg，點知冇翻過嚟一晚訓，連見都冇見過。<br />\n<br />\n到咗就嚟退宿嘅時間，我朋友好有衝勁想知道究竟roommate 係咩人<br />\n<br />\n佢打開佢啲筆記，見到一本學英文嘅生字簿，點知translate 出嚟嘅野勁cam，佢對於牛超級講究，對牛每個部位嘅英文都好熟悉，而且每種食物英文譯出嚟嘅中文都好奇怪，用簡體字寫。<br />\n<br />\n再一樣好笑嘅野係，我朋友再睇佢放喺度食譜，點知點食譜得圖畫，完全唔知本野點樣教煮野食。<br />\n<br />\n由嗰一刻開始，我朋友開始諗：<br />\n究竟呢個人喺邊個星球嚟嘅呢？"},{"pid":"51b993016c66df5fd0ed252d7a011fb216a699b6","tid":665182,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:08:46.000Z","msg":"有個咁嘅rm咪好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10921a9e5b795fb561fde526046d10a87113995b","tid":665182,"uid":165187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:11:03.000Z","msg":"so?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0ed8bf506302994e28b3e31c390a5df19d58af","tid":665182,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n10/10"}]}